{"tid":631820,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[燈神]球皇比利：尼馬可領巴西奪世盃","createTime":"2018-04-17T00:05:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-17T14:39:28.000Z","uid":35192,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"61b90c4a92fcb48fd65f9418e2242401878a086d","tid":631820,"uid":35192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T00:05:06.000Z","msg":"有「烏鴉嘴」之稱的球皇比利向來「貼嘜衰嘜」，近日比利又再次提到，希望尼馬可以把握今夏世盃這個絕佳機會，帶領巴西奪得世盃冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n「他將迎接第二次機會，上屆世盃期間他不幸地受傷，結果巴西災難性出局；我相信今屆是一個非常非常好的機會，讓尼馬捲土重來，他是一名好球員，我們即管放長雙眼看他為巴西贏得世盃。」比利續指：「每個人都知道，巴西擁有歐洲球會中最好最獨特的球員，毫無疑問他們能帶領巴西闖進世界盃決賽。」<br />\n<br />\n比利續指，世人總是會選擇一些熱門球隊如阿根延、英格蘭、西班牙等，但足球是充滿驚喜，在世盃每支球隊都有平等的機會，如意大利在世盃外出局一樣。"},{"pid":"95f6f05ad902a2e704dd5aea46b8d55391ef9613","tid":631820,"uid":29820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T00:11:17.000Z","msg":"好心佢收下把口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f5e5424fb0ae41094af7c5b2c05e8649fbd5f11","tid":631820,"uid":9581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T00:19:05.000Z","msg":"買冠軍可以諗少隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94288e0cdb17776c20b347c8b5db0c2b5d4a5879","tid":631820,"uid":81183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T00:21:46.000Z","msg":"比利係咪暗示唔睇好阿根庭，英撚，西班牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁樣祝福人都有"},{"pid":"2b30b115ff9552e01129ac2cc8b741031e9772ad","tid":631820,"uid":52006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"94288e0cdb17776c20b347c8b5db0c2b5d4a5879","tid":631820,"uid":81183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T00:21:46.000Z","msg":"比利係咪暗示唔睇好阿根庭，英撚，西班牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁樣祝福人都有"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018